OL,3,CBrief taste of spring before wet and
OL,4,Cwindy Easter weekend
OL,6,FThere's a subtle shift in the air this
OL,7,Fweek.
OL,9,FAfter a run of cooler, changeable
OL,10,Fconditions, we're briefly moving into
OL,11,Fsomething milder and more in line with
OL,12,Fwhat we hope this time of year might
OL,13,Ffeel like.
OL,15,FA reminder that Spring is trying to
OL,16,Fsettle in.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
