CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774894265
OL,3,CBrief taste of spring before wet and
OL,4,Cwindy Easter weekend
OL,6,FTemperatures will lift for a time,
OL,7,Fespecially across the south, where
OL,8,Fhighs could reach the mid to high
OL,9,Fteens. In any brighter spells, it
OL,10,Fshould feel pleasantly warm, a welcome
OL,11,Fcontrast to the recent chill.
OL,13,FBut unfortunately, this is a short-
OL,14,Flived change.
OL,16,FClouds will begin to build again, rain
OL,17,Freturns for some, and by the end of
OL,18,Fthe week, the pattern is already
OL,19,Fturning more unsettled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
