OL,3,CBrief taste of spring before wet and
OL,4,Cwindy Easter weekend
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThis is also the case as we head into
OL,12,Fthe Easter weekend, where the overall
OL,13,Fpicture is becoming clearer, although
OL,14,Fthere is still some uncertainty in the
OL,15,Fdetail.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
