OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774894265
OL,3,CBrief taste of spring before wet and
OL,4,Cwindy Easter weekend
OL,6,FIt is still a few days away, and
OL,7,Fthings can change, but at this stage,
OL,8,Flow pressure is likely to play a
OL,9,Fbigger role, bringing a more
OL,10,Fchangeable and unsettled feel to the
OL,11,Fweather.
OL,13,FWind, rain and brighter breaks
OL,15,FThere will be spells of rain at times,
OL,16,Fsome of them heavy, along with
OL,17,Fstrengthening winds, especially in
OL,18,Fmore exposed western and northwestern
OL,19,Fareas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
