PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774894265
OL,3,CBrief taste of spring before wet and
OL,4,Cwindy Easter weekend
OL,6,FThe Met Office is also pointing
OL,7,Ftowards a more unsettled picture, with
OL,8,Fwet and windy conditions likely at
OL,9,Ftimes through the weekend.
OL,11,FMet Office Meteorologist Steven Keates
OL,12,Fsays there is a strong signal for
OL,13,Fthese conditions to continue into
OL,14,FEaster, although some brighter spells
OL,15,Fare still expected, particularly
OL,16,Ftowards the southeast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
