PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774894265
OL,3,CBrief taste of spring before wet and
OL,4,Cwindy Easter weekend
OL,6,FIt won't be a complete washout. There
OL,7,Fwill be some sunshine at times, but
OL,8,Fthese brighter spells are likely to be
OL,9,Fmixed in with showers rather than
OL,10,Flasting for long.
OL,12,FA changeable feel, not a washout
OL,14,FThe southeast may see more in the way
OL,15,Fof drier, brighter weather at times,
OL,16,Fbut even here, that settled spring
OL,17,Ffeel is likely to stay just out of
OL,18,Freach.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
