PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774894265
OL,3,CBrief taste of spring before wet and
OL,4,Cwindy Easter weekend
OL,6,FSo while we do get a brief reminder of
OL,7,Fspring this week, Easter itself looks
OL,8,Fset to feel much more changeable.
OL,10,FA mix of sunshine, showers, wind and
OL,11,Frain, and very much a case of dressing
OL,12,Ffor all seasons.
OL,14,FSo if you're out hunting for Easter
OL,15,Feggs, you might need an umbrella and a
OL,16,Fwaterproof coat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
